{"id":"api/core/NgZoneOptions","title":"NgZoneOptions","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/NgZoneOptions\", \"name\": \"NgZoneOptions\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/change_detection/scheduling/ng_zone_scheduling.ts#L121-L172\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"ngzoneoptions\">NgZoneOptions<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions#ngzoneoptions\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e5bsp2ucm5b3x54cssgnmoss1\">用於設定事件並使用 <code><a href=\"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideZoneChangeDetection</a></code> 執行合併。</p>\n\n  </section><section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZoneOptions</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions#eventCoalescing\"><span class=\"member-name\">eventCoalescing</span>?: boolean</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions#runCoalescing\"><span class=\"member-name\">runCoalescing</span>?: boolean</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection\"><code>provideZoneChangeDetection</code></a></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n  \n  \n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a id=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>屬性</th>\n        <th>說明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"eventCoalescing\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">eventCoalescing</span>?: boolean</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"esm6cbgiipquc96c0k267fuje\">（可選）指定或不指定合併事件變更檢測。考慮以下情況。</p>\n          <code-example>\n&lt;div (click)=\"doSomething()\"&gt;\n  &lt;button (click)=\"doSomethingElse()\"&gt;&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1esyzsczi1ptbepxoj3p0lgvg\">單擊按鈕時，由於事件冒泡，將呼叫兩個事件處理程式，並觸發 2 次變更檢測。我們可以合併此類事件以僅觸發變更檢測一次。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"opuxkb1tam7k3oo5xjsad5su\">預設情況下，此選項將是 false。因此，事件將不會被合併，並且變更檢測將被觸發多次。如果此選項設定為 true，則變更檢測將透過排程動畫幀來非同步觸發。因此在上面的情況下，變更檢測將只會觸發一次。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"runCoalescing\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">runCoalescing</span>?: boolean</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9t3bps9m3r3ahpih477shlszu\">（可選）指定 <code><a href=\"api/core/NgZone\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZone</a>#run()</code> 方法呼叫是否應合併為單個變更檢測。</p>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"czk3su6u1np51ws2huk6ihka0\">考慮以下情況。</p>\n<code-example>\nfor (let i = 0; i &lt; 10; i ++) {\n  ngZone.run(() =&gt; {\n    // do something\n  });\n}\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1vof025w3hjhzx8xsfhd8810d\">這種情況會多次觸發變更檢測。使用 ngZoneRunCoalescing 選項，事件迴圈中的所有變更檢測只會觸發一次。此外，變更檢測是在 requestAnimation 中執行的。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/NgZone\n - api/core/NgZoneOptions#eventCoalescing\n - api/core/NgZoneOptions#instance-properties\n - api/core/NgZoneOptions#ngzoneoptions\n - api/core/NgZoneOptions#runCoalescing\n - api/core/NgZoneOptions#see-also\n - api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/change_detection/scheduling/ng_zone_scheduling.ts#L121-L172\n-->"}